I want to build a generic EventEmitter base class that all our services can extend. Right now only the TaskService needs events, but I'm sure other services will need them too. Here's my plan:

```javascript
class BaseEventEmitter {
  constructor() { this.listeners = {}; }
  on(event, cb) { (this.listeners[event] ||= []).push(cb); }
  emit(event, data) { (this.listeners[event] || []).forEach(cb => cb(data)); }
}

class TaskService extends BaseEventEmitter {
  createTask(data) {
    const task = this.repo.save(data);
    this.emit('task:created', task);
    return task;
  }
}
